## Quick Tips
- Always check mobile view first (Design → Responsive Design Mode in DevTools)
- Use Inspector (F12) to test CSS changes in real-time
- Reference color scheme: Purple (#6F42C1), Green (#198754), Red (#DC3545), Gray (#6C757D)
- Keep file sizes small: optimize images, minimize CSS
- Test across browsers: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge
